          "description": "I have been a patient of Dr. Sassan Rastegar for nearly thirty years, which in itself speaks to the consistency and excellence of care provided at this practice. Over the decades, Dr. Rastegar has demonstrated an unwavering commitment to precision, professionalism, and patient-centered care. His expertise is matched by his thoughtful approach\u2014he takes the time to explain treatments thoroughly, ensuring comfort, clarity, and trust at every visit.\n\nThe practice is exceptionally well-managed, with a warm and welcoming atmosphere that makes each appointment a positive experience. I would also like to recognize Sally, whose specialty in dental cleanings is truly outstanding. She is consistently meticulous, gentle, and attentive, bringing both skill and care to her work in a way that sets her apart.\n\nIt is rare to find a dental practice that maintains such a high standard over so many years. I am grateful for the continuity of care and would highly recommend Dr. Rastegar and his team to anyone seeking a dentist they can trust long-term.",
