          "description": "I\u2019m so lucky to have found a dental office in Manhattan that I truly trust. Sally, the hygienist, is wonderful - you can tell she genuinely cares about her patients and takes the time to get to know them. She and Dr. Rastegar are both extremely knowledgeable and explain everything clearly, which makes each visit comfortable and stress\u2011free. The entire office staff is incredibly friendly and welcoming, making appointments something I look forward to. If you are looking for a good dental office, look no further.",
