          "description": "I visited Midtown Dental Care for the first time my co-worker recommended it because she has been going there for many years. I went scared like many people are scared of the dentist. To be honest I find this a little pricey specially if your insurance doesn\u2019t cover much, but you feel like they are taking good care of you and they make you feel comfortable.\nThe first person I saw was my hygienist Sally she is great she really takes her time to ask you questions and answer any you might have, she also makes you feel at ease, she is very gentle when she is doing the cleaning so you suffer the least pain and discomfort possible\u2026 She seems to be great with people it comes normal to her.\nIf you looking for a hygienist ask for Sally.\n\nDadnery",
